Let me analyze the images and provide the solution:

- Total blocks: 6
- Layers: 3-4 layers high
- Colors used: Red, Green, Blue, Orange
- Structure has an arch/curved block at the bottom, square blocks in the middle, and triangular/peaked blocks on top

Block Dictionary Selection:
Required blocks with their indices:
1. Red arch block (Index 1)
2. Green rectangular block (Index 11)
3. Blue cubic block (Index 6)
4. Orange cylindrical block (Index 13)
5. Orange triangular peaked blocks (Index 14 and Index 15)

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 1 (red arch)
    Step2: Move block with index 11 (green rectangle)
    Step3: Move block with index 6 (blue cube)
    Step4: Move block with index 13 (orange cylinder)
    Step5: Move block with index 14 (orange peaked block)
    Step6: Move block with index 15 (orange peaked block)
}
